              />
              <figcaption class="review__caption">Mary Smith</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <div class="review__text">
              <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-small">
                She is an expert in hair color!
              </h3>
              <p>
                I've been coloring my hair for years and have visited numerous salons, but the color treatment I received at Sparkle Beauty Salon in Coral Springs is by far the best. The colorist understood exactly what I wanted and delivered beyond my expectations. The color is vibrant, rich, and perfectly suits my complexion. I've received so many compliments already. If you're considering a color change, Sparkle Beauty Salon is the place to go!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <div class="review">
            <figure class="review__shape">
              <img
                src="img/user-6.jpg"
                alt="Sparkle Salon Client"
                class="review__img"
              />
              <figcaption class="review__caption">Janet Wilson</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <div class="review__text">
              <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-small">
                WOW! My hair looks amazing
              </h3>
              <p>
                I visited Sparkle Beauty Salon in Coral Springs for the first time and I am beyond impressed! The transformation is unbelievable. My hair has never looked better. The shine, the bounce, the texture - everything is just perfect. I can't stop looking at myself in the mirror. A big shout out to the expert stylists at Sparkle Beauty Salon. You guys are truly magicians!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button
        class="carousel-control-prev"
        type="button"
        data-bs-target="carouselReview"
        data-bs-slide="prev"
      >
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
      </button>
      <button
        class="carousel-control-next"
        type="button"
        data-bs-target="carouselReview"
        data-bs-slide="next"
      >
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>
